# SOCIAL MEDIA API
# Django Social Media API

A professional DRF API with authentication, profile system, 
follow/unfollow, JWT authentication and swagger documentation.

## Features
✔ JWT Login / Register  
✔ Email OTP Verify  
✔ Profile Create / Update  
✔ Follow/Unfollow System  
✔ Private Profile Access  
✔ Swagger API Docs  
✔ DRF Spectacular Schema  

